Anthropic, OpenAI, Google DeepMind, Meta AI, Microsoft AI, Amazon (AWS AI), Apple AI, xAI, Mistral AI, Cohere, Scale AI, Cursor/Anysphere, Perplexity, Replit, Hugging Face.

